                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-item bg-light rounded p-4">
                <i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                <p>Posted 2 job openings and received 30+ applications in 48 hours. Simple but effective platform.</p>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <img class="img-fluid flex-shrink-0 rounded" src="/Images/profile.jpg" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                    <div class="ps-3">
                        <h5 class="mb-1 subheading">Fatma Ali</h5>
